{"tid":2288080,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"討論: 應否繼續使用「不推文回覆」？","createTime":"2020-11-16T08:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T13:41:46.000Z","uid":130698,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebdcdfe1a3e0467a03ae850b785cbedd012b898","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"首先，我唔係想admin取消呢個功能，而係user回覆時揀邊個好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我將帖文分做四類：<br />\nA: 社運/時事/突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB: 有益討論/求助/心理支援 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC: 鳩up/吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD: PR/風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAB類帖文都值得推，C有待商榷，D要拉<br />\n<br />\n社運期間用不推文令資訊集中喺熱門，呢個時期AB(60-85%) C(10%) D(5-30%)。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不推文令資訊集中喺熱門，一眼睇晒。唔使被 D類 垃圾/風向阻住，傳播有用資訊。<br />\n<br />\n但依加A(30%) B(15%) C(15%) D(40%)，使用不推文<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而會被PR/風向文推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為背後有ACssss 操縱住。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span class=\"gold\">一律使用「推文回覆」，令一般post浮返上黎，唔使睇到PR/風向文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/唔同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都歡迎討論～"},{"pid":"72b10d4fa3e77417c8e9321ab8b7f2e6ef310a09","tid":2288080,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"依家個問題好似係睇少人用不推文<br />\n果啲集中討論post/感情台/玩膠post 勁多人無用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fa0004cf90e14a542db57b74039af67448fe31","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72b10d4fa3e77417c8e9321ab8b7f2e6ef310a09","tid":2288080,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"依家個問題好似係睇少人用不推文<br />\n果啲集中討論post/感情台/玩膠post 勁多人無用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"多謝回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集中討論/感情台 我會歸類為B類， 屬於有益討論/分享生活，推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩膠 係D類，破壞良好討論，要拉，不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想全部人，除咗D類，一律停用「不推文回覆」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用返「推文回覆」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ed9462d6836bbe573a4a17f58705cc268f5aa7","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">ABC類帖文</span> 都係良性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"gold\">要推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">D類帖文</span> 五毛/分化/引戰/玩腸/業配(marketing) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\">要拉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1fefb7865101310fc19a7360848ed6bfb0af50","tid":2288080,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"首先要破除熱門要多正經post呢種迷信，屌人用推文回覆嘅撚樣要屌返佢轉頭，咁先可以真正拉到五毛/PR post"},{"pid":"bf6e5f3bce5adf149ecda11491d48441ca52d15e","tid":2288080,"uid":206594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得上到熱門就會多人click來睇認真topic<br />\n而家時事台一堆標題黨，一堆copy and paste嘅貼文，一堆亂咁highlight 紅色大字嘅新聞<br />\n又唔諗吓點解會開始無人理時事，又唔了解人性<br />\n淨係諗住用行政手段操控輿論"},{"pid":"493243ae107c9a84246ea8e806a33fd183ac4000","tid":2288080,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jkstudio.jasonkong/posts/2777437222267751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjkstudio.jasonkong%2Fposts%2F2777437222267751&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=a17e97b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jkstudio.jasonkong/posts/2777437222267751</a><br />\n<br />\n經典重溫<br />\n【連登如何用焦慮製造冷漠】<br />\n<br />\n唔係想潑你冷水<br />\n面對無力感，大家想逃避真係好撚符合人性<br />\n有啲位時機到自然會hit返<br />\n日日淨係關注關注，但又做唔到啲咩嗰陣，會加速人個麻木感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnqvD1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnqvD1Y.jpg&h=7f2f81d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢本書有詳細講<br />\n你可以唔認同佢建議大家唔再睇新聞<br />\n但佢分析點解點解追新聞會有反效果，人面對資訊氾濫嘅情況之下會有咩行為<br />\n好有參考價值"},{"pid":"4f0a010588d8abd3dfbf17dcccd4d18647ff045e","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c1fefb7865101310fc19a7360848ed6bfb0af50","tid":2288080,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"首先要破除熱門要多正經post呢種迷信，屌人用推文回覆嘅撚樣要屌返佢轉頭，咁先可以真正拉到五毛/PR post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"同意，A類帖重要，但BC類都同樣重要，生活係 8hrs+工作 + 8hrs娛樂組成，<span class=\"orange\">如果連登只有譴責冇支持，唔會有人想上</span><br />\n連登有愛<br />\n而D類 spam 同五毛式玩膠 太乞人憎，呢啲見一個report一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0732fd6b8b43b03989313350315e90b9b6a2e7e3","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf6e5f3bce5adf149ecda11491d48441ca52d15e","tid":2288080,"uid":206594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得上到熱門就會多人click來睇認真topic<br />\n而家時事台一堆標題黨，一堆copy and paste嘅貼文，一堆亂咁highlight 紅色大字嘅新聞<br />\n又唔諗吓點解會開始無人理時事，又唔了解人性<br />\n淨係諗住用行政手段操控輿論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"我想連登變返有正常討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而唔係洗版式推文，有少少深度討論都夠，好似巴打回覆咁。<br />\n更加唔想熱門充斥住spam (👈 亦都係我開po嘅主因)<br />\n時事同生活同樣重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335d7dffbe3e8bfcebc70a7841c95bc98b14ecbd","tid":2288080,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493243ae107c9a84246ea8e806a33fd183ac4000","tid":2288080,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jkstudio.jasonkong/posts/2777437222267751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjkstudio.jasonkong%2Fposts%2F2777437222267751&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=a17e97b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jkstudio.jasonkong/posts/2777437222267751</a><br />\n<br />\n經典重溫<br />\n【連登如何用焦慮製造冷漠】<br />\n<br />\n唔係想潑你冷水<br />\n面對無力感，大家想逃避真係好撚符合人性<br />\n有啲位時機到自然會hit返<br />\n日日淨係關注關注，但又做唔到啲咩嗰陣，會加速人個麻木感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnqvD1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnqvD1Y.jpg&h=7f2f81d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢本書有詳細講<br />\n你可以唔認同佢建議大家唔再睇新聞<br />\n但佢分析點解點解追新聞會有反效果，人面對資訊氾濫嘅情況之下會有咩行為<br />\n好有參考價值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗篇文啦，最尾兩點：大量垃圾資訊(D類)，拒絕任何論。正正係我想解決嘅嘢，亦係我開po嘅主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">我開